title: [Old Ta'Faendryl, West Woods]
description: The velvet dark shadows of the trees seem to converge and tremble as the path winds through and around them.  The brush bristles with tell-tale signs of life, chirping insects singing a night song from the leaf-littered woods floor.

The light-dappled shadows of the trees seem to converge and tremble as the path winds through and around them.  The woods bristle with tell-tale signs of life, chirping birds singing throatily from the leafy canopy overhead.
